    "text": "(Piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.939,
    "endTime": 32.836,
    "text": "(Singing) It was done"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.86,
    "endTime": 36.283,
    "text": "When the benediction had been sung"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.415,
    "endTime": 45.312,
    "text": "Firelight gently woke us from our golden night"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.111,
    "endTime": 48.669,
    "text": "My surprise"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.94,
    "endTime": 54.269999999999996,
    "text": "I can turn to see your open eyes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.681,
    "endTime": 60.306,
    "text": "And I know You are alive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.576,
    "endTime": 63.885,
    "text": "I know that smile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.306,
    "endTime": 67.608,
    "text": "Nothing more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.718,
    "endTime": 73.173,
    "text": "In the after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.197,
    "endTime": 76.974,
    "text": "There is waking from your sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.998,
    "endTime": 80.926,
    "text": "And your lover"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.95,
    "endTime": 84.321,
    "text": "Is the only face you see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.755,
    "endTime": 88.425,
    "text": "We are after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.449,
    "endTime": 91.687,
    "text": "Ever after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.178,
    "endTime": 94.868,
    "text": "There is laughter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.529,
    "endTime": 100.692,
    "text": "Afterneath"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.413,
    "endTime": 119.107,
    "text": "The war"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.131,
    "endTime": 122.902,
    "text": "Nobody ever even asked what for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.694,
    "endTime": 127.48400000000001,
    "text": "Up above"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.508,
    "endTime": 131.289,
    "text": "Nothing matters but the ones you love"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.75,
    "endTime": 134.968,
    "text": "So get out with me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.992,
    "endTime": 138.79,
    "text": "Now you've got enough with me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.814,
    "endTime": 142.18599999999998,
    "text": "Just the two of us you see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.805,
    "endTime": 146.393,
    "text": "And nothing more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.164,
    "endTime": 150.956,
    "text": "In the after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.98,
    "endTime": 154.714,
    "text": "There is waking from your sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.738,
    "endTime": 158.385,
    "text": "And your lover"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.409,
    "endTime": 161.394,
    "text": "Is the only face you see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.127,
    "endTime": 165.73100000000002,
    "text": "We are after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.755,
    "endTime": 169.484,
    "text": "Ever after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.509,
    "endTime": 175.862,
    "text": "There is laughter Afterneath"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.234,
    "endTime": 180.65,
    "text": "Oh, we after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.674,
    "endTime": 184.437,
    "text": "Ever after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.461,
    "endTime": 187.39600000000002,
    "text": "There is laughter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.42,
    "endTime": 193.434,
    "text": "Afterneath"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.62,
    "endTime": 199.633,
    "text": "Oh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.571,
    "endTime": 207.929,
    "text": "Oh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.914,
    "endTime": 216.265,
    "text": "Oh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.482,
    "endTime": 226.482,
    "text": "Oh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.944,
    "endTime": 231.125,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.15,
    "endTime": 235.302,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.326,
    "endTime": 236.477,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.501,
    "endTime": 238.377,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.401,
    "endTime": 239.55100000000002,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.363,
    "endTime": 242.781,
    "text": "I love a depressing song ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.805,
    "endTime": 243.806,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.83,
    "endTime": 244.98100000000002,
    "text": "you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.5,
    "endTime": 247.394,
    "text": "I've been writing them for 15 years now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.418,
    "endTime": 250.424,
    "text": "and to be honest, over that time,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.448,
    "endTime": 253.787,
    "text": "I've come to kind of believe that they're not really depressing at all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.196,
    "endTime": 257.478,
    "text": "In fact, I think they're kind of the most important songs we have."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.317,
    "endTime": 261.44100000000003,
    "text": "Songs that sing of sorrow,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.464,
    "endTime": 262.616,
    "text": "of grief,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.64,
    "endTime": 263.998,
    "text": "of longing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.22,
    "endTime": 266.18600000000004,
    "text": "of the darker side of love,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.21,
    "endTime": 268.64,
    "text": "the underside of being alive,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.665,
    "endTime": 271.507,
    "text": "these are the songs I just never tire of hearing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.531,
    "endTime": 273.742,
    "text": "and I never tire of writing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.766,
    "endTime": 275.865,
    "text": "because they make me feel less alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.973,
    "endTime": 280.298,
    "text": "They speak to a very real part of being human"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.322,
    "endTime": 282.943,
    "text": "that can often be hidden in fear and shame"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.967,
    "endTime": 285.541,
    "text": "and pushed deep down where it lingers and rots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.318,
    "endTime": 288.496,
    "text": "But I think in listening to these songs --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.521,
    "endTime": 290.6,
    "text": "really listening --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.624,
    "endTime": 295.14000000000004,
    "text": "can allow us to refeel these hard emotions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.38,
    "endTime": 297.306,
    "text": "but in a cathartic and healing way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.999,
    "endTime": 303.6,
    "text": "In a way that reminds us, as we listen, that we're not alone in darkness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.676,
    "endTime": 309.419,
    "text": "There's a Japanese phrase known as \"mono no aware,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.443,
    "endTime": 314.238,
    "text": "which roughly translates as \"the bittersweet poignancy of things,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.262,
    "endTime": 317.674,
    "text": "or the pathos or \"ahness\" of things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.428,
    "endTime": 321.515,
    "text": "It's a valuable awareness of impermanence,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.324,
    "endTime": 327.343,
    "text": "both a kind of gentle, transient sadness as things pass by in life,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.367,
    "endTime": 332.31,
    "text": "but also a deeper, softly lingering sadness"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.55,
    "endTime": 334.312,
    "text": "about the impermanence of all reality."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.939,
    "endTime": 339.925,
    "text": "\"Mono no aware\" can be manifest in lots of life stories and moments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.949,
    "endTime": 341.13800000000003,
    "text": "and songs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.162,
    "endTime": 345.334,
    "text": "One example in Japanese culture is the celebration of the cherry blossom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.262,
    "endTime": 349.358,
    "text": "The cherry blossom in and of itself is no more impressive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.382,
    "endTime": 352.47,
    "text": "than that of an apple or orange tree,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.494,
    "endTime": 354.90900000000005,
    "text": "but what sets it apart is its brevity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.564,
    "endTime": 358.389,
    "text": "Cherry blossoms fall within a single week --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.413,
    "endTime": 360.77000000000004,
    "text": "can be whisked away on the gentlest breeze --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.686,
    "endTime": 363.758,
    "text": "and it's this that makes it more beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.536,
    "endTime": 366.353,
    "text": "It's utterly fragile,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.377,
    "endTime": 368.87,
    "text": "and fragility gives life its poignancy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.918,
    "endTime": 371.25,
    "text": "Now, being a cheery chap,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.274,
    "endTime": 374.92,
    "text": "nothing speaks to me more than this, and --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.116,
    "endTime": 375.378,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.402,
    "endTime": 379.794,
    "text": "you know, I think it's been the essence of my songwriting for years,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.819,
    "endTime": 381.63100000000003,
    "text": "of what moves me to write,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.655,
    "endTime": 383.383,
    "text": "what inspires me to sing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.52,
    "endTime": 387.234,
    "text": "Because pain and grief and doubt,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.258,
    "endTime": 390.789,
    "text": "when it's made manifest in music, in song --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.814,
    "endTime": 394.504,
    "text": "when it's made beautiful in poetry and painting,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.97,
    "endTime": 398.644,
    "text": "it can build a community and a kinship"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.668,
    "endTime": 402.38,
    "text": "in the knowledge that we are none of us alone in darkness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.243,
    "endTime": 407.52,
    "text": "My next song is one that I call \"Killing Me,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.544,
    "endTime": 408.741,
    "text": "and as the name suggests,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.766,
    "endTime": 410.60900000000004,
    "text": "it's not a dance floor favorite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.633,
    "endTime": 411.633,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.658,
    "endTime": 414.471,
    "text": "But it isn't miserable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.73,
    "endTime": 417.12800000000004,
    "text": "It's full of love and hope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.176,
    "endTime": 420.192,
    "text": "And I think it exemplifies everything I've been talking about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.192,
    "endTime": 424.698,
    "text": "And it's the first song I've written from the perspective of somebody else,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.722,
    "endTime": 427.167,
    "text": "specifically my grandmother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.191,
    "endTime": 429.58,
    "text": "as she lives on without my late grandfather,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.412,
    "endTime": 432.715,
    "text": "as she experiences new things in her life --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.51,
    "endTime": 436.155,
    "text": "her grandchildren getting married,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.179,
    "endTime": 437.78,
    "text": "having their own children,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 437.804,
    "endTime": 438.953,
    "text": "speaking at TED --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.358,
    "endTime": 441.886,
    "text": "all the while she lives without,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.91,
    "endTime": 444.39700000000005,
    "text": "and all the while she misses her soul mate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.851,
    "endTime": 446.19,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.495,
    "endTime": 458.149,
    "text": "(Piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.83,
    "endTime": 469.417,
    "text": "(Singing) Sweetheart would you wake up today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.12,
    "endTime": 476.242,
    "text": "I promise you would recognize my faith"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.776,
    "endTime": 483.38300000000004,
    "text": "I want to show you how I've grown in this place"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.825,
    "endTime": 489.173,
    "text": "In this place I'm not alone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.542,
    "endTime": 492.287,
    "text": "And I know I'll be OK"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 493.248,
    "endTime": 500.58,
    "text": "But it's always harder When the winter comes to stay"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.82,
    "endTime": 506.714,
    "text": "And I can't help remember all the words I never said"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.87,
    "endTime": 516.696,
    "text": "And it's killing me That you're not here with me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.409,
    "endTime": 520.212,
    "text": "I'm living happily"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.861,
    "endTime": 523.385,
    "text": "But I'm feeling guilty"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525.429,
    "endTime": 531.333,
    "text": "And you won't believe The wonders I can see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 531.899,
    "endTime": 535.51,
    "text": "This world is changing me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.689,
    "endTime": 539.507,
    "text": "But I will love you faithfully."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.571,
    "endTime": 545.692,
    "text": "(Piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.477,
    "endTime": 552.161,
    "text": "Oh, everything is taller these days"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.37,
    "endTime": 560.616,
    "text": "Maybe I feel smaller and time rushes away"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.56,
    "endTime": 564.982,
    "text": "So much I could show you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 565.6,
    "endTime": 568.238,
    "text": "How all the great-grandchildren"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.262,
    "endTime": 573.5559999999999,
    "text": "Have been laughing like we did when we were young"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575.36,
    "endTime": 581.212,
    "text": "I've been laughing like we did when we were young"
  },
  {
